What You'll Learn

By the end of this program, you'll have the skills to build complete web applications

Backend Development

  • • Build RESTful APIs with Spring Boot
  • • Implement database operations with JPA
  • • Handle authentication and authorization
  • • Deploy applications to cloud platforms

Frontend Development

  • • Create responsive web interfaces with React
  • • Manage application state effectively
  • • Integrate with backend APIs
  • • Implement modern UI/UX patterns

DevOps & Cloud

  • • Deploy applications on AWS
  • • Implement CI/CD pipelines
  • • Monitor and scale applications
  • • Use containerization technologies

Database Management

  • • Design and optimize databases
  • • Work with SQL and NoSQL databases
  • • Implement data access patterns
  • • Handle data migrations

Microservices

  • • Design microservices architecture
  • • Implement event-driven systems
  • • Use Apache Kafka for messaging
  • • Build scalable distributed systems

Career Skills

  • • Version control with Git
  • • Agile development practices
  • • Code review and testing
  • • Interview preparation
